{"word":"αἰδοῖος","slug":"αἰδοῖος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n2254\" key=\"ai)doi=os\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αἰδοῖος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">αἰδώς</etym>) <sense id=\"n2254.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having a claim to regard, reverence</tr_>, or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">compassion</tr_> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἰδώς</foreign>), in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> </bibl> only of persons, sts. of gods, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θεῶν γένος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">44</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:257\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">257</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:394\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.394</biblScope> </bibl>; more freq. of human beings, as kings, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:402\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" h